<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" /><meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} /><title>Adult Family Home - Kirkland, WA</title><style>* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; } body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; } header { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; padding: 1rem 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; } .header-content { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; } .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; } nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: opacity 0.3s; } nav a:hover { opacity: 0.8; } .hero { background: linear-gradient(rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.7), rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.7)), url(/images/1.png); background-size: cover; background-position: center; color: white; padding: 6rem 20px; text-align: center; min-height: 500px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; } .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; } .hero p { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; } .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; } .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.3s; } .btn:hover { background-color: #0052a3; } .btn-secondary { background-color: #1B4F72; } .btn-secondary:hover { background-color: #133956; } .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; } .content-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; } .content-section h2 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.8rem; } .content-section h3 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.3rem; } .content-section p { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; } .image-float-left { float: left; width: 30%; max-width: 220px; margin: 0 1.5rem 1rem 0; border-radius: 8px; shape-margin: 10px; } .image-float-right { float: right; width: 30%; max-width: 220px; margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; shape-margin: 10px; } .content-section p { max-width: 100%; } .clearfix { overflow: auto; } .clearfix::after { content: ""; display: table; clear: both; } ul { margin: 1rem 0 0 1.5rem; color: #666; } ul li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; } .testimonials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; } .testimonial-card { background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2D5016; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); } .testimonial-card p { color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; } .testimonial-author { color: #2D5016; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; } .highlight-box { text-align: center; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 2rem; } .highlight-box h3 { color: #2D5016; } .highlight-box a { color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; } .highlight-box a:hover { text-decoration: underline; } .bottom-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem; } footer { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; } .footer-contact { margin-bottom: 1rem; } .footer-contact a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; } .footer-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }</style></head><body><header><div class="header-content"><div class="logo">Adult Family Home</div><nav><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/about">About</a><a href="/services">Services</a><a href="/faq">FAQ</a><a href="/news">News</a><a href="/contact">Contact</a><a href="/legal">Legal</a></nav></div></header><div class="hero"><h1>Safe, home‑like living with consistent caregivers and personalized care.</h1><p>A warm, family-like environment in Kirkland, Washington</p><div class="hero-buttons"><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6zOPC_-XkiE4FFxW-MbLW13HCLkGp7LDdFpJXXJlNcikH5Q/viewform?usp=header" class="btn" target="_blank">Schedule a Visit</a></div></div><div class="container"><div class="content-section"><h2>Welcome to Our Adult Family Home</h2><div class="clearfix"><img src="/images/1.png" alt="Front exterior - safe and welcoming" class="image-float-left"><p>We provide personalized, compassionate care for adults who need support with daily living. Our home offers a safe, comfortable environment where residents receive individualized attention and meaningful engagement. Every detail of our home is designed with resident safety and comfort in mind, from secure spaces to clear, well-lit pathways. We believe that a residential setting should feel like home—warm, welcoming, and filled with the comfort of family.</p></div></div><div class="content-section"><h3>Our Approach</h3><div class="clearfix"><img src="/images/4.png" alt="Caregiver assisting resident with dignity" class="image-float-right"><p>We believe care should be delivered with dignity, respect, and warmth. Every resident is treated as a valued member of our family, and we're committed to supporting their physical health, emotional well-being, and quality of life. Our approach centers on listening to each resident's needs, preferences, and goals. We work closely with families to understand what matters most and adjust our care approach accordingly. Whether it's honoring favorite meals, maintaining meaningful routines, or supporting personal interests, we tailor everything to the individual.</p></div></div><div class="content-section"><h3>Why Choose Us?</h3><div class="clearfix"><img src="/images/2.png" alt="Living room - calm and social space" class="image-float-left"><ul><li>Safe, comfortable home environment with 24/7 supervision</li><li>Personalized care plans tailored to individual needs</li><li>Experienced, compassionate caregivers</li><li>Nutritious, home-cooked meals</li><li>Social engagement and meaningful activities</li></ul><p>We understand that choosing a care setting is one of the most important decisions a family makes. That's why we focus on creating an environment where residents thrive—not just physically, but emotionally and socially. Our small community size means no resident is just a number; everyone receives the attention and personalization they deserve.</p></div></div><div class="content-section"><h3>What Families Say</h3><div class="testimonials"><div class="testimonial-card"><p>"My mother has thrived in this home. The care is attentive, the staff treats her like family, and I see her genuinely happy."</p><div class="testimonial-author">— Harry</div></div><div class="testimonial-card"><p>"The home feels warm and secure. My dad's needs are met with kindness and professionalism. I couldn't ask for more."</p><div class="testimonial-author">— Sally</div></div><div class="testimonial-card"><p>"This is the kind of place I want for my future. The residents are well cared for, and the team truly cares about each person."</p><div class="testimonial-author">— David</div></div><div class="testimonial-card"><p>"We felt supported from the first phone call through the admission and beyond. This is genuine, caring adult family home care."</p><div class="testimonial-author">— Ava</div></div></div></div><div class="highlight-box"><h3>Ready to Learn More?</h3><p style="margin: 1rem 0;">Explore our <a href="/about">about us</a>, <a href="/services">services</a>, <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>, or <a href="/contact">contact us</a> today to discuss how we can support your loved one.</p><div class="bottom-buttons"><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc6zOPC_-XkiE4FFxW-MbLW13HCLkGp7LDdFpJXXJlNcikH5Q/viewform?usp=header" class="btn" target="_blank">Schedule a Visit</a><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get in Touch</a></div></div></div><footer><div class="footer-contact"><a href="tel:425-123-4567" style="color: #fff;">425-123-4567</a> | <a href="mailto:contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com" style="color: #fff;">contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com</a> | 7am–7pm, 7 days a week</div><p>&copy; 2026 Adult Family Home. All rights reserved.</p><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><a href="/" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Back to Home</a></div></footer></body></html>
